{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"24770-thato-s-birthday-surprise","title":"Thato's Birthday Surprise","description":"It is one week until Thato’s Birthday. His mama tells him he will have a big surprise. What will it be?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Corinne  Lamoral-Rosmarin","Jodi  Houareau"],"illustrators":["Brad Cuzen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/24770-thato-s-birthday-surprise"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/399707/size3/bc3dde28d7810ab1f4020fb4e63320b1.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/399707/size6/bc3dde28d7810ab1f4020fb4e63320b1.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86032/size6/e01509a56f29fb1429ecc5cf86c83630.jpg","text":"It is one week until Thato’s birthday. \nThat’s seven whole days!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86033/size6/0c0704532e95acab8bc66c31946abdac.jpg","text":"3/20","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86034/size6/51c0c2a6f53c8a9b3ad20aaee1ecdb2f.jpg","text":"His mama says: \n“Your birthday present will be a BIG surprise!” \nThato wonders: what will it be?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86035/size6/8e6f07f4c9c268014c15652a1520205d.jpg","text":"5/20","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86036/size6/368db8c40dd3bf8c7348e188ddb95bed.jpg","text":"On Monday Thato thinks: \n“Maybe I will get giant wings \nso I can fly high in the sky like a bird…”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86037/size6/7835a6d4aa68ef103eb5d4d4003541d3.jpg","text":"7/20","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86038/size6/14bfc1e1134b9a5e35bd22e5fa05e034.jpg","text":"On Tuesday Thato thinks: \n“Maybe I will have a birthday \ncake as big as a house!”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86039/size6/2fab1aaaef1db9752a37efbc55eb50f5.jpg","text":"9/20","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86040/size6/ce3dd519962b67d6fdce4932d84e41cd.jpg","text":"On Wednesday Thato thinks: \n“Maybe I will get a rocket ship \nto whizz up to the moon.”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86041/size6/4be0d74ae88f6f281c7fa5b39c2bc253.jpg","text":"11/20","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86042/size6/72d66cab35bcd429228cc4f1462cbd85.jpg","text":"On Thursday Thato thinks: \n“Maybe I will get fins so I can swim \nunder the water like a fish.”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86043/size6/60473988cb62deed9270c8ff563b5b55.jpg","text":"13/20","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86044/size6/6ab283e2cd032763bdba6c04eacccff2.jpg","text":"On Friday Thato thinks: “Maybe I will get magic soccer \nboots and score a thousand goals!”","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86045/size6/362f8d78769673037a33bce702f44f66.jpg","text":"On Saturday Thato thinks: “Maybe I will get a key that opens a box filled with treasure!”","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86046/size6/16b84ff1e0c9a71587c4c865db68de2e.jpg","text":"On Sunday it is Thato’s birthday. Mama smiles and says: “Come and see your surprise!”","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86047/size6/aa2bee7687ecc2ad6153900dae0e547b.jpg","text":"It is the best present ever. Thato’s big brother Kudzai has come to visit all the way from the big city!","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86048/size6/b72ca5d2fa42c18018b3f09f99254748.jpg","text":"Thato smiles and smiles and his big brother lifts him up in the air and hugs him.\nKudzai asks: “What do you want to do for your birthday, little brother?”","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/131674/size6/ed5b1f4d41a43e9d7c8034bea8319c24.jpg","text":"And Thato knows exactly what they \nwill do the whole day long.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/86050/size6/a2fec78e9b7e0d44547a99da63bc9041.jpg","text":"20/20","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":219}}